Package algo.interpreter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ITProcess
    This is the interface for the translation of Tmcrl nodes in Abstract process
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ANDBond  
    CatchingEvent
    This is the intermediate catching event class that return an abstract process that has an action representing the intermediate catching message of the bpmn model
    EndEvent
    This is the end event class that given a node generates a process with an action that as isTau=true
    EVENTBASEDGBond  
    Polygon
    This is the Polygon class that represents a Polygon as a sequence process if the elements inside the node are more than 1, otherwise it returns the representation on the single node
    StartEvent
    This is the Start Event class that given a node generates a process with an empty action
    Task
    This is the Task class that generates from a node an abstract process that represents a task element of the bpmn model.
    Tmcrl
    Applies the Translation Function over the RPST object of a BPMN participant.
    XORBond
    This is the XORBond class that represents XORBOND as a external choice process (tau.P1 + tau.P2 + ... + tau.PN) if the elements inside the node are more than 1, otherwise it returns the representation on the single node
